# Claude Code Portable - Configuration (OPTIONAL)
#
# This file is NOT required. Without it, Claude Code will open your
# browser to log in with your Claude account (Pro/Max/Teams).
# Your login persists in the data/ folder on this drive.
#
# Only create a "config" file if you need one of these:
#   - API key authentication (instead of browser login)
#   - Custom API proxy / base URL
#   - Auth token for gateway setups
#
# To use: copy this file to "config" (no extension) and uncomment what you need.

# API key from https://console.anthropic.com/
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Custom API base URL (proxies, gateways, etc.)
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://api.anthropic.com

# Auth token (alternative to API key, for some proxy setups)
# ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=
